🐚 HOW TO CREATE SCRIPT (WRITE THIS IN PRACTICAL)
gedit soumya_add.sh

👉 Write code → Save → Close

Then:

chmod +x soumya_add.sh
./soumya_add.sh



➕ 1. ADDITION SCRIPT (soumya_add.sh)
#!/bin/bash

echo "Soumya - Addition Program"

echo "Enter first number:"
read a

echo "Enter second number:"
read b

sum=$((a + b))

echo "Sum = $sum"



